question:
If a 3'' by 3'' square is added at each successive stage, what will be the area of the rectangle at Stage 6, in square inches?

[asy]size(250); real textsize = 10pt;
draw(unitsquare);
draw(shift(1.5*right)*unitsquare);
draw(shift(2.5*right)*unitsquare);
